data.description:
Welcome to this charming brick ranch home in Coulwood Hills! Property is situated on a beautiful half-acre lot and tastefully renovated paying homage to the home's original details. The entry way welcomes you into dedicated dining space adjacent to spacious living room, overlooking backyard with patio. Attached cozy den functions great as a home office or playroom. Chef’s kitchen was completed in 2020 and features SS gas range, soft close cabinetry, granite countertops and walk-in pantry. Down the main hall you’ll find 3 nicely sized bedrooms and shared hall bath. Owners suite is complete with his and her closets, spacious vanity area and updated bathroom.

Seller takes pride in ownership and has made notable additions such as replacement windows and entry doors, Hardie Plank siding, hardwood laminate flooring, and designer lighting. Voluntary Neighborhood council has park, community pool, and social events throughout the year. Minutes to all major highways, airport, and uptown!
